(40, 4, 2, 11, 19, 8, 8, 'forty days and forty nights', 'Fasting and Sustenance Connection', 'Both passages emphasize a period of forty days and nights, highlighting the theme of divine sustenance during fasting. In Matthew, Jesus fasts and experiences hunger, while in 1 Kings, Elijah is strengthened by food for his journey.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
