(40, 4, 3, 18, 1, 9, 12, 'If thou be the Son of God', 'Testing of Faith', 'This connection highlights the theme of testing faith in both passages. In Matthew, the tempter challenges Jesus'' identity as the Son of God, while in Job, Satan questions Job''s loyalty to God, suggesting that his faith is contingent on his blessings.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
